BETA 1.0

Hot and Cold Studios (discord.gg/Kp9Wy5dBwJ) presents:
A new semi platform, survive the longest, and kill enemies game

Box Fight: You survive the longest and kill as many enemies as you can before you die

King of the Hill: Climb up to the top and survive as long as you can
